{"tid":1567991,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"心跳低至38上下，血壓上96，下45","createTime":"2019-09-14T07:58:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-06T08:59:57.000Z","uid":231413,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0e1900a345116ef5bf4d4f187a0cb66850bd27fd","tid":1567991,"uid":231413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T07:58:34.000Z","msg":"今年42歲，有運動習慣，無心臟疾病，有哮喘，呢個數字係咪好差？<br />\n<br />\n醫院依家唔俾我走呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe8f5efb6d79a21d7f45ef9981660d6fdfd27f2c","tid":1567991,"uid":234159,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:01:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日見！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ktW8Y1Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FktW8Y1Q.jpg&h=d39b859f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1veB7Va.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1veB7Va.jpg&h=d08508ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a7fdf704451bc7c2f5f3ffcc7232662207712104","tid":1567991,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T11:35:09.000Z","msg":"國家級運動員有機會去到呢個心跳，但你唔係，所以已經唔正常，屬於心率不正當中嘅心跳過緩<br />\n<br />\n利申：之前有心率不正"},{"pid":"626271290db0cb693977a717e667fc421b3999f2","tid":1567991,"uid":28668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T13:47:59.000Z","msg":"你運動到咩level先<br />\n<br />\n心跳慢原因眾多，除了是運動員正常現象外，也可是患冠心病警號，亦有可能由心臟退化引起。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b86193d60e9e61a6518814b00393880ce03956c1","tid":1567991,"uid":271807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e1900a345116ef5bf4d4f187a0cb66850bd27fd","tid":1567991,"uid":231413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T07:58:34.000Z","msg":"今年42歲，有運動習慣，無心臟疾病，有哮喘，呢個數字係咪好差？<br />\n<br />\n醫院依家唔俾我走呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T13:59:02.000Z","msg":"好低，有運動開都唔應該咁低，留院觀察喇"},{"pid":"0207f7ed9990b8e05fb4af04558170d6627e0e9f","tid":1567991,"uid":198137,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:01:53.000Z","msg":"咩事入院先"},{"pid":"fed7aa6d2e48d3869a6006fb16c42c93257d709e","tid":1567991,"uid":231413,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T12:16:42.000Z","msg":"好不容易，<br />\n尋日終於俾我出院，<br />\n暫時斷症係不明藥物過敏，<br />\n做左好多次心電圖，<br />\n星期三批准我落床活動，<br />\n但心跳一直都40-50，<br />\n血壓大約維持110，60<br />\n但情況穩定，到星期五我苦苦哀求<br />\n於是醫生就俾我走了。<br />\n要到10月中做個24小時心電圖，<br />\n先再作決定，<br />\n我雖然有運動習慣，<br />\n但都只係肥宅大叔喺緩跑徑跑幾K嗰種啫，<br />\n絕對不會係因為肥宅體能優秀所以有咁嘅心跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我係一個抑鬱焦慮症患者，<br />\n有固定精神科醫物，<br />\n另外有骨科止痛藥，<br />\n每晚飯後就會食藥，<br />\n但嗰晚食完藥無耐就頭暈、心口痛，標冷汗，<br />\n屋企人於是打999請救護車到場送院。<br />\n<br />\n之前其實都頭暈暈，<br />\n但又星期六有活動想出院，<br />\n所以出左呢個post，<br />\n但出完無耐已經又暈，<br />\n於是拋棄出院念頭，<br />\n專心攤抖，<br />\n到今日先覆post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47bc608474d9dec9f8b242f9221c47cbad7ebb22","tid":1567991,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T19:47:09.000Z","msg":"咁都夠膽出院，樓主唔驚死？"},{"pid":"4f57abfa8f8a3e8d624980368b4a8cf2ba2b7d32","tid":1567991,"uid":305718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T19:50:00.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借一借位<br />\n我係前線FA 我有嘢講<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1586083\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1586083</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"aeafe01efa75a2e6ea6b65c5e18181cd33723795","tid":1567991,"uid":231413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47bc608474d9dec9f8b242f9221c47cbad7ebb22","tid":1567991,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T19:47:09.000Z","msg":"咁都夠膽出院，樓主唔驚死？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T05:33:16.000Z","msg":"我其實怕痛怕苦唔怕死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果真係一下摜低就咁了結，<br />\n我真心唔驚。<br />\n如果真係要死，<br />\n俾我返屋企陪住啲貓死，<br />\n如果唔駛死，<br />\n困住醫院亦無咩意思，<br />\n因為醫生都未確定到病因，<br />\n無治癒方案，<br />\n留院只係駁住啲機一路觀察，<br />\n所以我先堅持出院既。"},{"pid":"884dc7220e1a75d13fae6a05bd499b98a8152634","tid":1567991,"uid":266231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:46:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8123ca31428b0afc579de0dd2bc3702df34f083d","tid":1567991,"uid":231413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"884dc7220e1a75d13fae6a05bd499b98a8152634","tid":1567991,"uid":266231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:46:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T12:06:43.000Z","msg":"一定,多謝你關心,<br />\n你都一樣要保重啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9ae2713046c501a3f68b587d1edf9928a8b1f29","tid":1567991,"uid":65365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T12:37:40.000Z","msg":"應該有做心電圖架喎，醫生未睇？"},{"pid":"3c1d62c991e225cd2a100df7b4e65412c2275a58","tid":1567991,"uid":276989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T12:41:02.000Z","msg":"即刻入手iw5 mon住啦"},{"pid":"9efdaf6ff9513587ca262f888660569070276d8b","tid":1567991,"uid":231413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9ae2713046c501a3f68b587d1edf9928a8b1f29","tid":1567991,"uid":65365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T12:37:40.000Z","msg":"應該有做心電圖架喎，醫生未睇？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T12:41:05.000Z","msg":"有啊，做左好多次心電圖，<br />\n但無做24小時心電圖。<br />\n<br />\n普通心電圖檢查無異常。"},{"pid":"2f83acff034321f59e204684ea36106ee316c382","tid":1567991,"uid":65365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9efdaf6ff9513587ca262f888660569070276d8b","tid":1567991,"uid":231413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9ae2713046c501a3f68b587d1edf9928a8b1f29","tid":1567991,"uid":65365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T12:37:40.000Z","msg":"應該有做心電圖架喎，醫生未睇？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T12:41:05.000Z","msg":"有啊，做左好多次心電圖，<br />\n但無做24小時心電圖。<br />\n<br />\n普通心電圖檢查無異常。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T12:46:33.000Z","msg":"Sinus brady？heart block都冇？"},{"pid":"4782d7c9d0d4e6eefe6e133c67fd3fc153783363","tid":1567991,"uid":231413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f83acff034321f59e204684ea36106ee316c382","tid":1567991,"uid":65365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9efdaf6ff9513587ca262f888660569070276d8b","tid":1567991,"uid":231413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9ae2713046c501a3f68b587d1edf9928a8b1f29","tid":1567991,"uid":65365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T12:37:40.000Z","msg":"應該有做心電圖架喎，醫生未睇？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T12:41:05.000Z","msg":"有啊，做左好多次心電圖，<br />\n但無做24小時心電圖。<br />\n<br />\n普通心電圖檢查無異常。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T12:46:33.000Z","msg":"Sinus brady？heart block都冇？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T13:28:21.000Z","msg":"呢啲咁專門名詞我唔明，<br />\n不過每次做完我都會問醫生：點呀？點呀？<br />\n然後佢每次都話無咩特別，<br />\n有時會叫我打側身做超聲波，<br />\n但都係話無咩特別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我跳血壓都持續低（留醫期間）<br />\n出院我都無check住了，<br />\n淨係多休息，<br />\n唔做劇烈運動就咁咋，<br />\n4/10返病房覆診，<br />\n到時問下醫生，<br />\n有無進一步跟進啦唯有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ab6d7ed74a00b5f927ae3dbe59cd8a45d994096","tid":1567991,"uid":313974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T20:25:44.000Z","msg":"你好耐冇上水<br />\n身體還好嗎？"},{"pid":"0dab09a87b7fa7450f7a7459688ca151afdfca94","tid":1567991,"uid":231413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ab6d7ed74a00b5f927ae3dbe59cd8a45d994096","tid":1567991,"uid":313974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T20:25:44.000Z","msg":"你好耐冇上水<br />\n身體還好嗎？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T04:04:58.000Z","msg":"你好呀<br />\n多謝關心，<br />\n我身體健康，<br />\n做左好多檢查，<br />\n結果醫生都係唔肯定咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但呢排都好生猛，<br />\n無再發生類似情況，<br />\n不過心情沈重....."},{"pid":"eef2bb608b586cc2dd2dad190cbe335f1472db12","tid":1567991,"uid":313974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0dab09a87b7fa7450f7a7459688ca151afdfca94","tid":1567991,"uid":231413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ab6d7ed74a00b5f927ae3dbe59cd8a45d994096","tid":1567991,"uid":313974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T20:25:44.000Z","msg":"你好耐冇上水<br />\n身體還好嗎？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T04:04:58.000Z","msg":"你好呀<br />\n多謝關心，<br />\n我身體健康，<br />\n做左好多檢查，<br />\n結果醫生都係唔肯定咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但呢排都好生猛，<br />\n無再發生類似情況，<br />\n不過心情沈重....."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T08:59:57.000Z","msg":"冇事就好<br />\n唔好太擔心啦<br />\n多保重"}]}